# Shared Configuration Packages

This project uses several shared configuration packages to maintain consistency across the monorepo.

## TypeScript Configuration
[packages/typescript-config/](mdc:packages/typescript-config) contains shared TypeScript configurations.

## Tailwind Configuration
[packages/tailwind-config/](mdc:packages/tailwind-config) contains the shared Tailwind CSS configuration.

## ESLint Configuration
[packages/eslint-config/](mdc:packages/eslint-config) contains shared ESLint rules and settings.

## Usage
These configurations are referenced in the respective configuration files of each application and package, ensuring consistency throughout the project.

